name: Main Street Yield
description: Main Street Finance is excited to launch a new strategy for the msY Vault that leverages box spreads on the Chicago Mercantile Exchange (CME). This strategy aims to provide investors with attractive, stable yields in a tokenized format, making sophisticated TradFi opportunities accessible to a broader audience. Much like Ethena, which has gained popularity by funding futures speculators through its basis trade, the msY Vault funds options demand from retail and institutional players.
